Finding experiments¶

To use incense we first have to instantiate an experiment loader that will enable us to query the database for specific runs.

QuerySet([Experiment(id=25, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=26, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=27, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=29, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=30, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=31, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=32, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=33, name=autoencoder_test)])
